FOLLOW INSTRUCTION BELOW.

install database: 
create schema:
-------------
  data base scripts are located at resources\data.sql
  Data and scemal sql are renamed to .txt.
     

create certificates:
-------------------

Public keys is required for resource
command is
keytool -list -rfc --keystore keystore.jks | openssl x509 -inform pem -pubkey -noout

this required pubkey. download openssl


TEST:
----
clientid is the username
secret is the password 

test in dev env:
---------------
curl -u clientId:secret -X POST localhost:9000/oauth/token -d grant_type=password -d username=user -d password=pass


test in test env: (tekmlai.com)
---------------
curl -u clientId:secret -X POST https://oauth.tekmlai.com/oauth2server/oauth/token -d grant_type=password -d username=user -d password=pas


